COULD_YOU_REPEAT_THE_ORIGINAL_REQUEST.message: An ndéanfá an t-iarratas céanna arís?

DENY_0.message: I'm sorry, but I don't think I can trust you with this delivery.

DENY_1.message: Tar ar ais nuair a bheidh na cáilíochtaí cearta agat.

DENY_2.message: Ní dóigh liom gur tusa an píolóta atá mé ag lorg.

DENY_3.message: You don't look like someone I can trust with this delivery.

DENY_4.message: Ní dóigh liom gur tusa an sórt píolóta atá mé ag lorg.

DENY_5.message: Déarfainn nach bhfuil go leor taithí agat chun tasc chomh tábhachtach seo a dhéanamh.

DENY_6.message: Níor chuala mé riamh fútsa. Tá píolóta a bhfuil seantaithí aige ag teastáil uaim don seachadadh seo.

DENY_7.message: Nílim sásta dul sa seans leis an seachadadh seo agus é a thabhairt do dhuine ar bheagán taithí.

EXCELLENT_I_WILL_LET_THE_RECIPIENT_KNOW_.message: Ar fheabhas! Déarfaidh mé leis an bhfaighteoir go bhfuil tú ar an mbealach.

FLAVOUR_0_ADTEXT.message: GOING TO the {system} system? Money paid for delivery of a small package.

FLAVOUR_0_FAILUREMSG.message: Do-ghlactha amach is amach! Shíl mé nach dtiocfadh an pacáiste riamh. Nílim sásta íoc as.

FLAVOUR_0_INTROTEXT.message: Hi, I'm {name}. I'll pay you {cash} if you will deliver a small package to {starport} in the {system} ({sectorx}, {sectory}, {sectorz}) system, a distance of {dist} ly.

FLAVOUR_0_SUCCESSMSG.message: Go raibh maith agat as an seachadadh. Íocadh an méid iomlán leat.

FLAVOUR_0_WHYSOMUCHTEXT.message: Nuair a thug cara cuairt orm, d'fhág sí éadaí agus roinnt leabhar páipéir ársa ina diaidh. Ba mhaith liom iad a thabhairt ar ais di.

FLAVOUR_1_ADTEXT.message: CÚNAMH AG TEASTÁIL: Pacáiste a sheachadadh chuig réaltchóras {system}.

FLAVOUR_1_FAILUREMSG.message: Nílim sásta gur tháinig mo phacáiste chomh mall sin, agus diúltaím an costas a íoc.

FLAVOUR_1_INTROTEXT.message: Dia dhuit, is mise {name}. D'íocfainn {cash} as pacáiste a sheachadadh chuig {starport} i réaltchóras {system} ({sectorx}, {sectory}, {sectorz}), {dist} solasbhliain ar shiúl.

FLAVOUR_1_SUCCESSMSG.message: Fuair mé an pacáiste agus íocadh an méid iomlán leat.

FLAVOUR_2_ADTEXT.message: PRÁINNEACH: Long ghasta ag teastáil le pacáiste a sheachadadh chuig réaltchóras {system}.

FLAVOUR_2_FAILUREMSG.message: I was quite clear about the deadline and am very disappointed by the late delivery. You will not be paid.

FLAVOUR_2_INTROTEXT.message: Dia dhuit, is mise {name}. D'íocfainn {cash} as pacáiste a sheachadadh chuig {starport} i réaltchóras {system} ({sectorx}, {sectory}, {sectorz}), {dist} solasbhliain ar shiúl.

FLAVOUR_2_SUCCESSMSG.message: Íocadh an méid iomlán leat as an seachadadh. Go raibh maith agat.

FLAVOUR_2_WHYSOMUCHTEXT.message: Togra taighde atá ann, agus caithfear é a sheachadadh roimh an spriocdháta nó ní bhfaighimid aon mhaoiniú.

FLAVOUR_3_ADTEXT.message: SEACHADADH. Cáipéisí chuig réaltchóras {system}. Íocfar píolóta a bhfuil taithí aige/aici {cash}.

FLAVOUR_3_FAILUREMSG.message: Useless! I will never depend on you again! Needless to say, you will not be paid for this.

FLAVOUR_3_INTROTEXT.message: Dia dhuit, is mise {name}. D'íocfainn {cash} as pacáiste a sheachadadh chuig {starport} i réaltchóras {system} ({sectorx}, {sectory}, {sectorz}), {dist} solasbhliain ar shiúl.

FLAVOUR_3_SUCCESSMSG.message: Is mór agam do sheirbhís thráthúil dhiscréideach. Íocadh an méid iomlán leat.

FLAVOUR_3_WHYSOMUCHTEXT.message: Some extremely sensitive documents have fallen into my hands, and I have reason to believe that the leak has been traced to me.

FLAVOUR_4_ADTEXT.message: SEIRBHÍS PHOIST. Tá long ag teastáil uainn leis an bpost a sheachadadh chuig réaltchóras {system}.

FLAVOUR_4_FAILUREMSG.message: Your ship registration has been noted, we will reject all further applications for work from you.

FLAVOUR_4_INTROTEXT.message: Greetings. This is an automated message from Bedford and {name} Courier Services. We pay {cash} for the run to {starport} in the {system} ({sectorx}, {sectory}, {sectorz}) system, a distance of {dist} ly.

FLAVOUR_4_SUCCESSMSG.message: Is mór agam do sheirbhís thráthúil dhiscréideach. Íocadh an méid iomlán leat.

FLAVOUR_4_WHYSOMUCHTEXT.message: Bheimis lánsásta níos lú airgid a thabhairt duit.

FLAVOUR_5_ADTEXT.message: MOVING HOME. Move of hardware to {starport} from storage.

FLAVOUR_5_FAILUREMSG.message: What are these? Oh, you took so long that I forgot I'd even sent this!

FLAVOUR_5_INTROTEXT.message: Nice to meet you. I am {name} and I'm willing to pay {cash} for someone with a ship to help me move my belongings to {starport}. No rush, they are just some leftovers from moving house.

FLAVOUR_5_SUCCESSMSG.message: Thar barr. Tosóidh mé ag díluchtú láithreach. GRMA arís.

FLAVOUR_5_WHYSOMUCHTEXT.message: An mórán é? Ba chóir dom athsmaoineamh a dhéanamh ar mo thairiscint!

FLAVOUR_6_ADTEXT.message: CÚIRÉIR GEARR-RAOIN. Pacáiste beag a sheachadadh chuig {starport}.

FLAVOUR_6_FAILUREMSG.message: I could have delivered it faster myself. I'm not paying you.

FLAVOUR_6_INTROTEXT.message: Dia dhuit. Is mise {name} agus tabharfaidh mé {cash} duit as an bpacáiste seo a sheachadadh chuig {starport}.

FLAVOUR_6_SUCCESSMSG.message: Go raibh maith agat as an pacáiste. Íocadh an méid iomlán leat.

FLAVOUR_6_WHYSOMUCHTEXT.message: I don't think it's a lot.

FLAVOUR_7_ADTEXT.message: LASTA IDIRPHLÁINÉADACH. Lasta áitiúil a iompar go dtí {starport}.

FLAVOUR_7_FAILUREMSG.message: Ní bheidh ár gcustaiméirí róshásta leis seo. Ná bí ag súil le híocaíocht!

FLAVOUR_7_INTROTEXT.message: Hello. We need these crates delivered to {starport} as soon as possible. Standard payment for this shipment is {cash}.

FLAVOUR_7_SUCCESSMSG.message: Excellent, we've credited the funds into your account.

FLAVOUR_7_WHYSOMUCHTEXT.message: Rátaí caighdeánacha, oibrímid leis an margadh.

FLAVOUR_8_ADTEXT.message: SEACHADADH ÁITIÚIL. Beart a sheachadadh chuig {starport} go tapaidh.

FLAVOUR_8_FAILUREMSG.message: You were offered a premium for quick delivery! I refuse to pay for this.

FLAVOUR_8_INTROTEXT.message: My name is {name} and I need this item delivered to a friend at {starport} pronto, I'll pay you {cash} credits if you get it there in a reasonable time.

FLAVOUR_8_SUCCESSMSG.message: Your prompt delivery is appreciated, I have credited your account accordingly.

FLAVOUR_9_ADTEXT.message: COR PACÁISTE. Earraí somheata a sheachadadh chuig {starport} go práinneach.

FLAVOUR_9_FAILUREMSG.message: Tá sé millte, agus níl maith ar bith ann! Ní bhfaighidh tú cianóg rua uainn.

FLAVOUR_9_INTROTEXT.message: Greetings, we're behind with our produce shipment and need it delivered to {starport} urgently. We'll pay you {cash} for your troubles.

FLAVOUR_9_SUCCESSMSG.message: Iontach! Tosóimid ag díphacáil láithreach. Nuashonróidh mé do chuntas lom díreach.

FLAVOUR_9_WHYSOMUCHTEXT.message: Tá ár slí bheatha ag brath air.

HOW_SOON_MUST_IT_BE_DELIVERED.message: Cé chomh luath agus is gá dom é a sheachadadh?

IT_COULD_BE_DANGEROUS_YOU_SHOULD_MAKE_SU.message: D'fhéadfadh sé a bheith contúirteach. Ba chóir duit deimhniú go bhfuil tú ullamh.

NOT_ANY_MORE_THAN_USUAL.message: Ní bheidh ach mar is gnáth.

PIRATE_TAUNTS_0.message: Beidh aithreachas ort as déileáil le {client}

PIRATE_TAUNTS_1.message: Dealraíonn sé gur tháinig mo phá!

PIRATE_TAUNTS_2.message: Tá tú ag obair do {client}? Ba dhrochsmaoineamh é sin.

PIRATE_TAUNTS_3.message: Do lasta agus do bheo, a phíolóta!

PIRATE_TAUNTS_4.message: Tá mé cinnte go bhfaighfear pingin mhaith airgid air seo ar an margadh

PIRATE_TAUNTS_5.message: Níl an t-ádh ort inniu! Abair d'urnaí.

PIRATE_TAUNTS_6.message: Tell my old friend {client} that I'll see them in hell!

PIRATE_TAUNTS_7.message: That package isn't going to reach its destination today.

PIRATE_TAUNTS_9.message: You'll pay for that cargo, with your life.

THIS_IS_A_VALUABLE_PACKAGE_YOU_SHOULD_KE.message: This is a valuable package, you should keep your eyes open.

THIS_IS_VERY_RISKY_YOU_WILL_ALMOST_CERTA.message: Tá contúirt mhór ann, agus beidh troid mhór romhat gan dabht.

WHY_SO_MUCH_MONEY.message: Cén fáth a bhfuil an méid sin airgid i gceist?
